casebody.data:
Dionte Jermaine DAVIS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
FLORIDA DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2104 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 14, 2017 SUAREZ, LOGUE and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Petitioner is deemed insolvent and may proceed in forma pauperis for purposes of this cause.

Upon consideration, this proceeding is dismissed for lack of jurisdiction, without prejudice to refile in the Second Judicial Circuit in and for Leon County, Florida.
